68
00:07:43,212 --> 00:08:01,262
Pope & AI: Pope Leo XIV published the first papal encyclical on AI: "Magnifica humanitas" – Anthropic co-founder Chris Olah responded publicly that external moral voices are indispensable for AI labs, as commercial interests often dominate internally .

69
